(14, 1, '2026-05-20 19:56:26', '2026-05-20 18:56:26', '<label> Vaše ime\n    [text* your-name autocomplete:name] </label>\n\n<label> Vaša e-pošta\n    [email* your-email autocomplete:email] </label>\n\n<label> Zadeva\n    [text* your-subject] </label>\n\n<label> Vaše sporočilo (neobvezno)\n    [textarea your-message] </label>\n\n[submit \"Pošlji\"]\n[_site_title] \"[your-subject]\"\n[_site_title] <nejc.toplak@dijaki.sers.si>\nOd: [your-name] [your-email]\nZadeva: [your-subject]\n\nSporočilo:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis is a notification that a contact form was submitted on your website ([_site_title] [_site_url]).\n[_site_admin_email]\nReply-To: [your-email]\n\n0\n0\n\n[_site_title] \"[your-subject]\"\n[_site_title] <nejc.toplak@dijaki.sers.si>\nSporočilo:\n[your-message]\n\n-- \nThis email is a receipt for your contact form submission on our website ([_site_title] [_site_url]) in which your email address was used. If that was not you, please ignore this message.\n[your-email]\nReply-To: [_site_admin_email]\n\n0\n0\nVaše sporočilo je bilo poslano. Hvala vam.\nMed pošiljanjem vašega sporočila je prišlo do napake. Poskusite znova kasneje.\nV enem ali več poljih je napaka. Preverite in poskusite znova.\nMed pošiljanjem vašega sporočila je prišlo do napake. Poskusite znova kasneje.\nPreden lahko pošljete sporočilo, se morate strinjati s pogoji uporabe.\nIzpolnite to polje.\nVnos v tem polju je predolg.\nVnos v tem polju je prekratek.\nMed nalaganjem datoteke je prišlo do neznane napake.\nDatotek te vrste ni dovoljeno nalagati.\nNaložena datoteka je prevelika.\nMed nalaganjem datoteke je prišlo do napake.', 'Kontaktni obrazec 1', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'kontaktni-obrazec-1', '', '', '2026-05-20 19:56:26', '2026-05-20 18:56:26', '', 0, 'http://localhost/trgovina/wordpress/?post_type=wpcf7_contact_form&p=14', 0, 'wpcf7_contact_form', '', 0),
